Context: The resume workshop at George Brown College will help students learn about creating effective resumes and cover letters, marketing themselves to employers, and navigating Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS). The workshop registration can be done on GBCareas, with the deadline for early registration encouraged. Students can contact ask.george@georgebrown.ca for inquiries or visit the college's Social Media Hub. The contact numbers for general inquiries are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. Please note that information on this website is subject to change without notice, and students should verify George Brown College fee requirements.
